Package: libofx4
Version: 0.9.0
Revision: 1
Description: OFX Library
License: GPL
Maintainer: Dave Reiser <dbreiser@users.sourceforge.net>
Source: mirror:sourceforge:libofx/libofx-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: 6e2172f0117f90805590bf755190b79e
GCC: 4.0
Depends: <<
  %N-shlibs (= %v-%r),
  libcurl4-shlibs, 
  libssh2.1-shlibs,
  libxml++1-shlibs (>= 1.0.4-1001), 
  libxml2-shlibs
<<
BuildDepends: <<
  gettext-bin, 
  gettext-tools, 
  libcurl4, 
  libgettext3-dev,  
  libiconv-dev, 
  libssh2.1,
  libxml++1 (>= 1.0.4-1001), 
  libxml2,
  opensp4 (>= 1.5.1-1002),
  opensp4-dev (>= 1.5.1-1002), 
  pkgconfig,
  system-openssl-dev
<<
BuildDependsOnly: True  
Conflicts: libofx, libofx1, libofx3
Replaces: libofx, libofx1, libofx3
ConfigureParams: --with-opensp-includes=%p/include/OpenSP --with-opensp-libs=%p/lib --disable-doxygen --enable-html-docs --disable-dependency-tracking
SetCPPFLAGS: -I%p/lib/system-openssl/include
SetLDFLAGS: -L%p/lib/system-openssl/lib
CompileScript: <<
 ./configure %c
 make LIBOFX_DTD_DIR=%p/share/%n-%v/dtd
<<
InstallScript: <<
 make install DESTDIR=%d LIBOFX_DTD_DIR=%p/share/%n-%v/dtd
<<
DocFiles: README COPYING
Splitoff: <<
  Package: %N-shlibs
  Depends: libgettext3-shlibs, libiconv, opensp4-shlibs (>= 1.5.1-1002)
  Files: <<
    lib/libofx.4.0.0.dylib
    lib/libofx.4.dylib
    share/%N-%v
  <<
  DocFiles: COPYING
  Shlibs: <<
    %p/lib/libofx.4.dylib 5.0.0 %n (>= 0.9.0-1)
  <<
<<
DescDetail: <<
LibOFX library is an API designed to allow applications to 
very easily support OFX command responses, usually provided by financial
institutions. It adds OFX support to GnuCash and AqBanking.
<<
HomePage: http://libofx.sourceforge.net/

 	  	 
